                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.014/11–2945: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Robertson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-11-29T20:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 29, 1945—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1915. As War Dept desires to proceed at earliest possible date with mapping
                    operations outlined in Dept’s 1776, Nov 1, 4 p.m. please inform us at once of
                    results of your approach to Chinese authorities.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
